Dialogue: 10,0:00:03.23,0:00:05.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I'm so full.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:05.86,0:00:06.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I think I ate too much.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:06.94,0:00:09.15,Default,,0,0,0,,You {\i1}did{\i0} have two hamburgers.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:09.15,0:00:12.20,Default,,0,0,0,,That's because Mashiro was paying.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:12.20,0:00:14.77,Default,,0,0,0,,That aside, it sure has been awhile.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:14.77,0:00:16.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Has it been two? Three months?
Dialogue: 10,0:00:16.12,0:00:17.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't remember.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:17.28,0:00:19.70,Default,,0,0,0,,At any rate, today we start \Nworking as a team again.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.28,0:00:20.75,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\1c&H323E5F&\blur1.003\fs50.139\frz-13\fax0.21\move(464,137.715,580,137.715,29,3449)}Mashiro
Dialogue: 10,0:00:19.70,0:00:20.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:25.38,0:00:27.18,Default,,0,0,0,,We should probably clean up first, huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:00:27.18,0:00:28.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:28.42,0:00:29.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry.
