Dialogue: 10,0:02:01.26,0:02:02.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:02.06,0:02:03.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:03.09,0:02:04.77,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the character design.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:04.77,0:02:05.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:08.27,0:02:14.83,Default,,0,0,0,,A con artist detective who sets up \Ntraps for criminals to discover the truth.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:16.40,0:02:17.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:17.24,0:02:17.99,Default,,0,0,0,,This is pretty interesting.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:17.99,0:02:18.82,Default,,0,0,0,,You think so?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:18.82,0:02:19.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks hard to pull off, though.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:19.70,0:02:20.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:21.20,0:02:23.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I realized this as I was writing.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:23.06,0:02:25.41,Default,,0,0,0,,A mystery doesn't really \Nhave a whole lot of action.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:25.87,0:02:28.16,Default,,0,0,0,,It's mostly dialogue while \Nthey solve the mysteries.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:28.16,0:02:31.68,Default,,0,0,0,,If it's all just flashy battles, it \Nwon't feel like a proper mystery.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:32.00,0:02:33.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, you're right.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:33.65,0:02:36.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I ran into the same problem \Nwriting my name, so I stopped.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:36.54,0:02:37.63,Default,,0,0,0,,You wrote a name?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:37.63,0:02:38.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:38.09,0:02:39.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me see.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:39.51,0:02:40.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Um—
Dialogue: 10,0:02:42.39,0:02:43.56,Default,,0,0,0,,But—
Dialogue: 10,0:02:44.14,0:02:45.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I only did a little bit.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:45.06,0:02:46.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Whatever, just show me.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:46.31,0:02:48.39,Default,,0,0,0,,We're working together again, aren't we?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:48.39,0:02:49.24,Default,,0,0,0,,C'mon.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:50.19,0:02:52.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Remember, I just did a little bit of the beginning.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:55.11,0:02:57.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Make the culprit think the \Nman he killed is still alive,
Dialogue: 10,0:02:57.61,0:03:00.20,Default,,0,0,0,,and when he comes back to kill him again—
Dialogue: 10,0:03:00.74,0:03:04.33,Default,,0,0,0,,This has been done before, but I \Nthink it'll work nicely as a hook.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:05.12,0:03:07.91,Default,,0,0,0,,It's good to have the main character \Nin action right from the start, too.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:07.91,0:03:10.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Woah, your drawings are great!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:10.11,0:03:11.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Way better than Takagi's.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:12.25,0:03:13.87,Default,,0,0,0,,The story is more important in a name.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:13.87,0:03:14.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, yeah.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:16.17,0:03:16.88,Default,,0,0,0,,With this—
Dialogue: 10,0:03:16.88,0:03:17.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:17.46,0:03:20.01,Default,,0,0,0,,You think it's okay to have a main \Ncharacter who can transform?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:20.01,0:03:20.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:20.72,0:03:24.96,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a manga and he's supposed to be a \Ncon artist, so we should get away with it.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:25.76,0:03:27.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Transform into what?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:27.85,0:03:29.84,Default,,0,0,0,,The person who was \Nsupposed to have been killed.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:29.84,0:03:32.81,Default,,0,0,0,,So our main character becomes \Nthe bait to lure out the culprit.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:32.81,0:03:34.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:34.33,0:03:38.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, he {\i1}is{\i0} the main character, so he should \Nhave at least one or two special abilities.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:38.20,0:03:40.45,Default,,0,0,0,,That'll definitely be more interesting.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:40.99,0:03:44.87,Default-Alt,,0,0,0,,He can change anything, even \Nhis gender, to fool the culprit.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:42.78,0:03:45.41,Default-Italic,,0,0,0,,I knew they worked better as a team.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:44.87,0:03:47.29,Default-Alt,,0,0,0,,That's perfect for a con artist!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:49.20,0:03:51.74,Default,,0,0,0,,We just need something after this.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:51.74,0:03:55.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, we just need a con with some \Ntraps that'll surprise the readers.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:56.50,0:03:58.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I couldn't come up with anything.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:58.67,0:04:01.14,Default,,0,0,0,,If we can do that, it could be really interesting.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:03.13,0:04:04.34,Default,,0,0,0,,This could work.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:04.34,0:04:06.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to write this more than \Nanything we've done before.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:06.93,0:04:07.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go with this,
Dialogue: 10,0:04:08.15,0:04:09.97,Default,,0,0,0,,and get it serialized for sure this time.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:09.97,0:04:10.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:12.44,0:04:14.04,Default,,0,0,0,,But six months, huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:14.04,0:04:14.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:15.23,0:04:16.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Ten names in six months.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:17.86,0:04:20.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Saiko, six months is our limit, right?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:21.44,0:04:23.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you saying you want more time?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:23.78,0:04:25.87,Default,,0,0,0,,No, that's not it.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:26.49,0:04:31.50,Default,,0,0,0,,To be honest, about a week after I told \NHattori that I was writing a mystery—
Dialogue: 10,0:04:33.33,0:04:34.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Be right there.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:36.08,0:04:37.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Sign here, please.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:37.44,0:04:38.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Six boxes?!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:39.59,0:04:43.05,Default,,0,0,0,,And all stuffed {\i1}full{\i0} of mystery novels and DVDs.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:43.05,0:04:44.63,Default,,0,0,0,,There was a note, too.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:45.22,0:04:47.64,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't always avoid similarities, so don't worry.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:47.64,0:04:48.84,Default,,0,0,0,,It's all about how you pull it off.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:49.35,0:04:51.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Use this to brush up on your skills.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:54.06,0:04:57.91,Default,,0,0,0,,It would take me at least two \Nmonths just to go through all of it.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:58.27,0:04:59.65,Default,,0,0,0,,But you probably should, right?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:00.15,0:05:03.14,Default,,0,0,0,,The important things for a \Nmystery are the tricks and the story,
Dialogue: 10,0:05:03.14,0:05:05.41,Default,,0,0,0,,so going through it all would definitely help.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:05.78,0:05:08.24,Default,,0,0,0,,You came up with a great character,
Dialogue: 10,0:05:08.24,0:05:10.89,Default,,0,0,0,,so I want to do the same with the story.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:10.89,0:05:14.51,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why I figured we should \Nprobably spend a little more time on this.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:17.00,0:05:18.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:18.67,0:05:21.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I think you're right.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:22.13,0:05:26.85,Default,,0,0,0,,It won't matter whether we have a good \Ncharacter or not if the story isn't interesting.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:27.30,0:05:28.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Saiko?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:28.14,0:05:30.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I always make a big deal \Nabout working on my drawings,
Dialogue: 10,0:05:30.97,0:05:33.32,Default,,0,0,0,,so of course you'd want to \Nreally work on your story, too.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:33.93,0:05:35.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm fine if you want to do—
Dialogue: 10,0:05:35.27,0:05:36.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll do it.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:36.56,0:05:37.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:37.21,0:05:39.86,Default,,0,0,0,,All those novels and DVDs.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:39.86,0:05:42.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll go through them all and \Nwrite down summaries for you.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:42.61,0:05:46.74,Default,,0,0,0,,That way it'll save you the time and \Nyou can keep working on your name.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:46.74,0:05:50.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Your success is my dream too, after all.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:50.21,0:05:50.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Your dream?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:50.99,0:05:52.29,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened to cellphone novels?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:52.29,0:05:53.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I gave that up.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:53.04,0:05:53.74,Default,,0,0,0,,That was fast!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:53.74,0:05:57.15,Default,,0,0,0,,You should really think more \Nbefore deciding what to do.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:57.15,0:05:59.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Helping you guys is a lot better than \Nspending my time writing a cellphone novel
Dialogue: 10,0:05:59.71,0:06:01.92,Default,,0,0,0,,that I'm not even sure will sell or not, isn't it?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:02.55,0:06:05.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess it {\i1}would{\i0} be a big help if you \Nwrote down just the important parts.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:05.92,0:06:06.80,Default,,0,0,0,,In that case—
Dialogue: 10,0:06:06.80,0:06:07.52,Default,,0,0,0,,But—
Dialogue: 10,0:06:07.97,0:06:10.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Novels and movies both have a certain atmosphere,
Dialogue: 10,0:06:10.95,0:06:12.68,Default,,0,0,0,,so I think it would be better to do it yourself.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:13.39,0:06:16.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Each person sees the story \Nin their own unique way.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:16.18,0:06:17.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess you're right.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:17.69,0:06:19.27,Default,,0,0,0,,But if you do that, you \Nwon't have enough time to—
Dialogue: 10,0:06:19.27,0:06:20.61,Default,,0,0,0,,It's alright.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:20.61,0:06:23.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess I was just trying to rush it.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:23.94,0:06:27.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Azuki already made her debut \Nand is starting to get popular,
Dialogue: 10,0:06:27.95,0:06:29.91,Default,,0,0,0,,so I kinda felt like I was being left behind.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:30.99,0:06:32.17,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why—
Dialogue: 10,0:06:32.49,0:06:33.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Trying to get an anime by the time we're 18 is—
Dialogue: 10,0:06:33.91,0:06:34.66,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't give up!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:35.19,0:06:37.96,Default,,0,0,0,,That doesn't sound like you at all.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:38.50,0:06:41.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, why are you crying?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:42.42,0:06:43.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I—
Dialogue: 10,0:06:43.63,0:06:47.81,Default,,0,0,0,,This last month, while you \Ntwo weren't working together,
Dialogue: 10,0:06:48.13,0:06:49.73,Default,,0,0,0,,was really tough.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:50.13,0:06:52.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought it was partially my fault,
Dialogue: 10,0:06:52.85,0:06:55.02,Default,,0,0,0,,but I was more worried about you two.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:55.43,0:06:55.97,Default,,0,0,0,,And—
Dialogue: 10,0:06:55.97,0:06:58.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I was worried about Miho, too.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:58.85,0:07:05.41,Default,,0,0,0,,The thing I want most right now is\N for you and Miho to get married.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:06.98,0:07:08.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks, Miyoshi.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:09.03,0:07:11.36,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll get our manga turned into an anime,
Dialogue: 10,0:07:11.36,0:07:13.05,Default,,0,0,0,,have Azuki play the heroine,
Dialogue: 10,0:07:13.05,0:07:14.21,Default,,0,0,0,,and then get married.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:15.24,0:07:18.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if it's only a little bit, \NI'll be glad to accept your help.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:22.75,0:07:25.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I finally got Mashiro to understand how I feel!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:25.38,0:07:27.12,Default,,0,0,0,,But you're still gonna cry about it?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:27.12,0:07:29.93,Default,,0,0,0,,If everything works out, let's get married too.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:30.26,0:07:31.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you talking about me and you?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:31.55,0:07:32.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Who else would I be talking about?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:32.55,0:07:34.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you proposing to me or something?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:34.68,0:07:36.18,Default,,0,0,0,,You said you loved me, didn't you?!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:36.18,0:07:36.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:36.82,0:07:38.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I said I 'like' you, but I don't \Nremember ever using the word 'love.'
Dialogue: 10,0:07:38.39,0:07:39.93,Default,,0,0,0,,We even kissed!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:39.93,0:07:42.90,Default,,0,0,0,,W—What the hell are you \Ndoing saying that in front of Saiko?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:46.65,0:07:47.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Takagi!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:48.15,0:07:50.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Here are the summaries I did yesterday.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:50.03,0:07:51.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:51.49,0:07:52.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's get going.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:52.61,0:07:54.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, I forgot my bag.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:54.12,0:07:56.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold on, I'll be right back.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:57.99,0:07:59.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Miyoshi's sure getting into this, huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:00.08,0:08:02.99,Default,,0,0,0,,It's already been a month and she's \Nbeen at it every day, hasn't she?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:02.99,0:08:06.02,Default,,0,0,0,,She's summarizing it a lot better \Nthan I thought she would, too.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:06.02,0:08:06.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Um—
Dialogue: 10,0:08:06.67,0:08:07.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:07.96,0:08:08.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Me?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:09.13,0:08:10.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:10.01,0:08:10.72,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:11.55,0:08:12.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Takagi.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:13.63,0:08:15.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you and Miyoshi from class three
Dialogue: 10,0:08:16.47,0:08:17.51,Default,,0,0,0,,going out?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:18.10,0:08:20.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, and apparently we're getting married, too.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:22.85,0:08:24.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Is he serious?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:24.73,0:08:25.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:25.44,0:08:26.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I've got a fiancé, too.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:26.61,0:08:28.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Doesn't everybody?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:38.70,0:08:39.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Mashiro.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:39.82,0:08:40.41,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:40.41,0:08:42.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Tomorrow's November 5th.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:42.61,0:08:43.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you know what day it is?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:43.62,0:08:45.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Azuki's birthday.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:45.12,0:08:46.73,Default,,0,0,0,,You remembered, huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:46.73,0:08:48.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry, I'll send her a message.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:48.63,0:08:50.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that all?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:50.09,0:08:52.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Love comes in many forms, dontcha know.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.89,0:08:58.76,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\pos(80,427.852)\fnArial\frz12.5\b1\fax0.2\fscx75\fry-10\fs26.741\blur1.003\c&H48B6CF&}St. Visual's\NGirls Academy
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.27,0:09:06.27,Cellphone,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.003\fs56.824\pos(680,153.759)\frz8.2\fax0.05\c&H88756D&}Mashiro Moritaka
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.27,0:09:06.27,Cellphone,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.337\fs66.852\pos(280,508.074)\frz8.2\fax0.045\c&H988176&}Happy birthday.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:07.98,0:09:09.44,Default,,0,0,0,,That's all you wrote?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:09.44,0:09:10.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Yep.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:10.65,0:09:11.65,Default,,0,0,0,,What about a present?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:11.65,0:09:13.61,Default,,0,0,0,,It's enough to let her know I care.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:13.61,0:09:15.75,Default,,0,0,0,,For now, we're focusing on \Nour names until next spring.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:15.75,0:09:17.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm—
Dialogue: 10,0:09:17.11,0:09:19.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess love does come in all different forms.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:19.33,0:09:23.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh yeah, "St. Viz Girls" was popular \Nenough that it got a second season.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:23.91,0:09:25.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:25.19,0:09:27.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I haven't been watching lately, so I didn't know.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:27.29,0:09:29.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I got a message about it.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:29.31,0:09:31.88,Default,,0,0,0,,And Miho said she's going \Nto be singing the ending.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:32.71,0:09:34.46,Default,,0,0,0,,She didn't tell me that.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:34.46,0:09:37.71,Default,,0,0,0,,It looks like the recording studio's \Nproducer took a special interest
Dialogue: 10,0:09:37.71,0:09:40.02,Default,,0,0,0,,and is having the three most \Npopular girls sing the ending.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:40.02,0:09:41.64,Default,,0,0,0,,It was a spur of the moment decision.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:41.64,0:09:43.02,Default,,0,0,0,,That's great!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:43.02,0:09:45.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Azuki really is on her way to \Nbeing a full-fledged idol, isn't she?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:45.94,0:09:50.66,Default,,0,0,0,,She also told me to make sure \Nthat Mashiro doesn't see it.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:51.11,0:09:52.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Why is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.12,0:10:10.25,InsertSong,,0,0,0,,Do you want to say it or will you hold back?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.25,0:10:17.42,InsertSong,,0,0,0,,Please don't hide the feelings deep in your heart.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:11.21,0:10:13.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Azuki really sucks at singing.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:13.19,0:10:16.22,Default,,0,0,0,,This explains why I could \Nnever get her to go to karaoke!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:17.38,0:10:19.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, my stomach!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.42,0:10:20.26,InsertSong,,0,0,0,,Let them all out.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.59,0:10:23.68,InsertSong,,0,0,0,,I'm lonely and I want to see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.68,0:10:28.52,InsertSong,,0,0,0,,I'm so sad that I might break.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:27.69,0:10:30.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Their skirts are so short.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.52,0:10:32.44,InsertSong,,0,0,0,,I want you to look only at me.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:30.42,0:10:31.73,Default,,0,0,0,,This is kind of exciting.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:31.73,0:10:34.28,Default,,0,0,0,,It's supposed to make you want to look, so of \Ncourse they're wearing something underneath, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.44,0:10:36.90,InsertSong,,0,0,0,,Into my heart, never wavering.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:34.28,0:10:36.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, but still—
Dialogue: 10,0:10:36.28,0:10:38.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I bet you're in shock, huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:38.07,0:10:39.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.07,0:10:42.03,InsertSong,,0,0,0,,Your touch, your gaze, your body.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:39.12,0:10:42.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Thinking about other people watching her like this—
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.03,0:10:45.58,InsertSong,,0,0,0,,My heart aches just looking at you.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:43.24,0:10:48.96,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I was just thinking that I can see Azuki \Nworking hard, but Azuki can't see me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.62,0:10:49.21,InsertSong,,0,0,0,,What are you waiting for?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.21,0:10:52.71,InsertSong,,0,0,0,,Please tell me.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:49.29,0:10:50.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't you send her a picture?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:50.53,0:10:51.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Want me to take one?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:51.13,0:10:52.25,Default,,0,0,0,,No, stop it!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:52.25,0:10:52.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.71,0:10:58.59,InsertSong,,0,0,0,,The more I yearn for you, the farther you seem to get.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:53.20,0:10:55.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I—It's embarrassing.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:55.42,0:10:56.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:56.05,0:10:58.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Miho says to keep you from watching \Nand now you're embarrassed?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.59,0:11:00.47,InsertSong,,0,0,0,,It's driving me mad.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:59.18,0:11:00.51,Default,,0,0,0,,You guys are so weird.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.48,0:11:02.85,InsertSong,,0,0,0,,It's going to be a tearful
Dialogue: 10,0:11:00.51,0:11:03.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Love comes in many forms, dontcha know.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.85,0:11:07.18,InsertSong,,0,0,0,,Daybreak Symphony.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:14.32,0:11:15.39,Default-Italic,,0,0,0,,Azuki
Dialogue: 10,0:11:16.27,0:11:17.99,Default-Italic,,0,0,0,,really is cute.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:23.91,0:11:25.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Here you are.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:26.54,0:11:28.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Please take one.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:31.79,0:11:33.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello, this is Takagi.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:33.44,0:11:34.79,Default,,0,0,0,,How's the story coming along?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:34.79,0:11:38.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I'm working on it, but if I'm going \Nto spend the next two years on this,
Dialogue: 10,0:11:38.34,0:11:42.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought I should go through all \Nthe material you sent me first.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:42.01,0:11:43.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:43.00,0:11:44.51,Default,,0,0,0,,You must have your hands full.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:44.51,0:11:46.81,Default,,0,0,0,,No, it's a big help.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:47.14,0:11:48.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm actually watching one right now.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:49.85,0:11:51.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm glad it's coming in handy.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:51.97,0:11:55.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Take your time and let me \Nknow when you finish a name.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:55.23,0:11:56.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I will.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:57.11,0:12:01.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks to you watching that \Nright now, I think he bought it.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:02.57,0:12:03.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Miyoshi, turn off the TV.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:03.60,0:12:04.53,Default,,0,0,0,,It's Hattori.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:04.53,0:12:06.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, alright.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:06.91,0:12:08.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi Hattori.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:09.45,0:12:10.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Good, thanks.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:11.54,0:12:14.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I'm having a little trouble with the name.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:14.92,0:12:16.63,Default,,0,0,0,,But I'll do my best.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:18.42,0:12:21.92,Default-Italic,,0,0,0,,Mashiro and Takagi are \Nboth taking their time.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:22.47,0:12:25.80,Default-Italic,,0,0,0,,I'll call them into the office when they \Nboth have something finished and—
Dialogue: 10,0:12:25.80,0:12:26.89,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:26.89,0:12:28.94,Default,,0,0,0,,You were doing a mystery, too?!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:30.27,0:12:33.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, it looks like we both had the same idea.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:38.82,0:12:41.19,Default-Italic,,0,0,0,,Then they'll join forces
Dialogue: 10,0:12:41.19,0:12:42.91,Default-Italic,,0,0,0,,and Ashirogi Muto will be reborn!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:44.86,0:12:46.62,Default-Italic,,0,0,0,,It's all going according to plan.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:48.62,0:12:49.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Heishi.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:49.62,0:12:50.72,Default,,0,0,0,,How are they?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:50.72,0:12:52.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Niizuma said his parents grew these themselves.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:57.42,0:12:59.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Here you are.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:00.05,0:13:02.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Please take one.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.18,0:13:09.01,Handwriting,,0,0,0,,{\1c&H696969&\blur1.003\fax-0.15\fscy90\move(1024,218.606,550,218.606,0,3817)}"Detective Trap" (Tentative)
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.18,0:13:09.01,Handwriting,,0,0,0,,{\1c&H696969&\blur1.003\fax-0.15\fscy90\move(940,340.944,466,340.944,0,3817)}Serialization Name (3)
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.18,0:13:09.01,Handwriting,,0,0,0,,{\1c&H696969&\blur1.003\fax-0.15\fscy90\move(920,461.278,446,461.278,0,3817)}Ashirogi Muto
Dialogue: 10,0:13:06.39,0:13:09.01,Default-Italic,,0,0,0,,Eight names for serialization, huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:09.60,0:13:12.60,Default,,0,0,0,,We had planned on bringing in ten chapters,
Dialogue: 10,0:13:12.60,0:13:13.90,Default,,0,0,0,,but we didn't make it in time.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:15.52,0:13:18.06,Default,,0,0,0,,You didn't tell me you'd be coming together.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:18.06,0:13:18.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:19.61,0:13:21.58,Default,,0,0,0,,How long have you guys been back together?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:21.90,0:13:25.87,Default,,0,0,0,,We got back together about a month after you \Nasked me to go two years without saying anything.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:26.49,0:13:27.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:28.41,0:13:29.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess you got me.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:30.08,0:13:34.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I guess I'll just take it as proof \Nthat you two make a good team.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:34.87,0:13:37.96,Default,,0,0,0,,It's all thanks to you that we \Nwere able to get back together.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:38.75,0:13:41.46,Default,,0,0,0,,You stopped me from doing the \Ndrawings for a different series
Dialogue: 10,0:13:41.46,0:13:45.01,Default,,0,0,0,,and told Takagi that I was working \Non a detective story as well.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:45.76,0:13:46.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:52.43,0:13:54.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright then, let me have a look.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:54.62,0:13:55.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:27.72,0:14:29.30,Default,,0,0,0,,W—What do you think?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:32.35,0:14:33.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I like it.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:33.67,0:14:34.72,Default,,0,0,0,,This is really great.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:35.56,0:14:38.28,Default,,0,0,0,,You guys really pulled one over me here.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:39.27,0:14:41.61,Default,,0,0,0,,And you really can't wait until \Nyou're finished with high school?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:41.61,0:14:42.82,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:42.82,0:14:46.84,Default,,0,0,0,,If you really think it's good, please submit \Nit for the next serialization meeting.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:47.40,0:14:52.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I've said this already, but there's really no reason \Nto get serialized while you're still in high school.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:52.02,0:14:53.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Niizuma is doing it, isn't he?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:53.78,0:14:55.38,Default,,0,0,0,,And he's working by himself.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:58.83,0:15:01.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Fine, but with two conditions.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:02.42,0:15:03.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Conditions?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:03.48,0:15:08.13,Default,,0,0,0,,One, you submit this as a one-shot for the \Nnext "Golden Future Cup" and it does well.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:08.59,0:15:09.88,Default,,0,0,0,,The "Golden Future Cup?"
Dialogue: 10,0:15:09.88,0:15:11.80,Default,,0,0,0,,That's in the summer, right?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:11.80,0:15:13.94,Default,,0,0,0,,And one more thing before that.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:15.18,0:15:20.31,Default,,0,0,0,,You have to bring me a 19 page \Nstory for this series every two weeks.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:20.85,0:15:22.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Even though we're not getting serialized yet?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:22.69,0:15:24.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:24.19,0:15:26.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Real serialization is once every week,
Dialogue: 10,0:15:26.17,0:15:30.40,Default,,0,0,0,,but you have the "Golden Future Cup" to \Ndo and you don't have any assistants yet,
Dialogue: 10,0:15:30.40,0:15:31.96,Default,,0,0,0,,so you don't have to do a completed manuscript.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:32.57,0:15:36.21,Default,,0,0,0,,A good rank in the "Golden Future Cup" and \Nan unfinished manuscript every two weeks.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:36.54,0:15:39.71,Default,,0,0,0,,If you can meet these conditions, I'll \Nsubmit this for the serialization meeting.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:39.71,0:15:42.63,Default-Italic,,0,0,0,,No matter how you look at \Nit, that seems a bit harsh.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:42.63,0:15:43.29,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll do it!!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:43.29,0:15:43.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:45.42,0:15:47.89,Default,,0,0,0,,And you won't be turning these \Nnames into finished manuscripts.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:47.89,0:15:51.30,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll be making new, unfinished \Nmanuscripts of this level once every two weeks.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:51.30,0:15:56.31,Default,,0,0,0,,When you finish one, you'll bring it in \Nand have a meeting for the next chapter.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:56.76,0:15:59.06,Default,,0,0,0,,So this is a rehearsal for actual serialization?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:59.06,0:15:59.91,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:59.91,0:16:01.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you usually do this sort of thing?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:01.88,0:16:02.95,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:04.10,0:16:06.41,Default,,0,0,0,,But this is how I want to do it this time.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:06.77,0:16:10.07,Default,,0,0,0,,If you can't do this much, there's no way \Nyou can do it while still in high school.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:10.78,0:16:14.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, but you guys are not Niizuma.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:15.16,0:16:18.32,Default,,0,0,0,,And writing a detective manga is completely \Ndifferent than writing a battle manga.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:18.91,0:16:23.67,Default,,0,0,0,,And even if you don't get this serialized, \Nit will be a good experience for you.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:30.17,0:16:31.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:32.59,0:16:36.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I never thought that you \N worried about us so much.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:37.51,0:16:39.60,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll definitely show you we can do this
Dialogue: 10,0:16:40.22,0:16:42.17,Default,,0,0,0,,and then get serialized for sure.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:43.00,0:16:43.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Good.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:43.92,0:16:46.86,Default,,0,0,0,,If you can pull this off, even \Nthe higher-ups can't say no.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:47.31,0:16:50.57,Default,,0,0,0,,After all, this is really interesting.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:53.82,0:16:56.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Finally looks like we'll be considered, huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:56.65,0:17:01.08,Default,,0,0,0,,But before that, we've got the "Golden \NFuture Cup" and a chapter every two weeks.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:01.58,0:17:03.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I can manage with the story,
Dialogue: 10,0:17:03.25,0:17:04.79,Default,,0,0,0,,but do you think you can manage with the drawings?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:04.79,0:17:06.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll do it even if it kills me.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:06.92,0:17:07.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:07.96,0:17:10.22,Default,,0,0,0,,We've made it this far, so we can't stop now.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:12.76,0:17:13.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:13.88,0:17:15.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, Fukuda.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:15.68,0:17:17.09,Default-Alt,,0,0,0,,Hey, didn't expect to see you here.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:16.05,0:17:17.09,Default-Italic,,0,0,0,,Fukuda?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:17.59,0:17:21.23,Default-Italic,,0,0,0,,Is this the guy Saiko met when \Nhe was working at Eiji's place?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:17.59,0:17:18.74,Default-Alt,,0,0,0,,Here for a meeting?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:18.74,0:17:21.23,Default-Alt,,0,0,0,,Yeah, we just finished and are on our way home.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:21.72,0:17:22.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:23.56,0:17:25.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Takagi, Mashiro's partner.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:25.84,0:17:27.95,Default,,0,0,0,,You're the writer, huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:28.40,0:17:29.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:29.90,0:17:31.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you have a meeting, too?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:31.81,0:17:32.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:32.83,0:17:36.31,Default,,0,0,0,,My recent one-shot came in seventh.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:36.31,0:17:39.74,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not as good as I'd wanted, but \Nthe characters were interesting,
Dialogue: 10,0:17:39.74,0:17:45.37,Default,,0,0,0,,so Yujiro asked me to rework it with the same\N ones and try it out in the "Golden Future Cup."
Dialogue: 10,0:17:45.37,0:17:46.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Man,
Dialogue: 10,0:17:46.25,0:17:48.06,Default,,0,0,0,,what a pain.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:48.06,0:17:50.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to be a serialized author, already.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:50.46,0:17:51.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Us too.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:51.63,0:17:52.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:52.46,0:17:58.24,Default,,0,0,0,,We were just told to try our story out in the "Golden \NFuture Cup" before getting it serialized as well.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:58.24,0:17:58.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:58.98,0:18:00.76,Default,,0,0,0,,You were already accepted \Nfor the "Golden Future Cup?"
Dialogue: 10,0:18:00.76,0:18:02.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, it hasn't actually been accepted yet,
Dialogue: 10,0:18:02.68,0:18:06.49,Default,,0,0,0,,but our editor said that the way it is \Nnow, it should get accepted for sure.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:06.89,0:18:09.94,Default,,0,0,0,,There are only four or five people\N who get chosen for that, right?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:09.94,0:18:12.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Whatever, I'll make sure mine gets accepted too.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:12.65,0:18:15.65,Default,,0,0,0,,If it doesn't, Yujiro's gonna pay!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:16.95,0:18:17.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:17.53,0:18:18.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:18.16,0:18:21.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I may have lost to you guys in "Next,"
Dialogue: 10,0:18:21.66,0:18:25.21,Default,,0,0,0,,but I'll beat you for sure this time, Ashirogi Muto.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:31.50,0:18:33.25,Default,,0,0,0,,No, we'll make sure to win!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:33.25,0:18:33.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Good.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:33.96,0:18:35.88,Default,,0,0,0,,It's no fun otherwise.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:35.88,0:18:38.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's make it a fair fight.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:38.53,0:18:42.58,Default,,0,0,0,,And the winner will be that \Nmuch closer to number one.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:42.58,0:18:44.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Sound good to you?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:44.36,0:18:45.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:46.77,0:18:49.94,Default-Italic,,0,0,0,,Alright, first step is to get first \Nin the "Golden Future Cup."
Dialogue: 10,0:18:50.44,0:18:51.82,Default-Italic,,0,0,0,,We'll make sure to win!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:05.16,0:19:06.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, this is good.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:08.12,0:19:09.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright, let's talk about chapter two.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:09.79,0:19:10.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:13.21,0:19:16.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you finish the name for chapter \Nthree by the time school gets out today?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:16.42,0:19:19.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I'll have it ready to turn into a \Nmanuscript by the time we get home.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:19.01,0:19:20.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Slow down!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:21.93,0:19:23.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Here's the manuscript for chapter three.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:23.44,0:19:25.14,Default,,0,0,0,,And the name for chapter four.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:25.64,0:19:27.39,Default,,0,0,0,,We made it this time, too!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:30.31,0:19:31.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Good job.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:32.60,0:19:36.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Make sure you bring in the name for the \N"Golden Future Cup" one-shot next time.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:36.46,0:19:37.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:57.05,0:19:59.80,Default,,0,0,0,,You won't get serialized if you're \Nnot accepted into the contest.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:00.42,0:20:02.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Take your time and make this even better.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:03.55,0:20:04.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:08.52,0:20:10.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't this explanation a bit too long?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:10.31,0:20:11.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm—
Dialogue: 10,0:20:11.66,0:20:13.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll try shortening it a little.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:14.52,0:20:18.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you think we should make the main \Ncharacter look more exciting on the last page?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:18.02,0:20:19.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm—
Dialogue: 10,0:20:20.07,0:20:21.25,Default,,0,0,0,,You're probably right.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:21.25,0:20:22.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll redraw it.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:22.82,0:20:23.91,Default,,0,0,0,,What should we do about the title?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:23.91,0:20:24.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:24.45,0:20:27.19,Default,,0,0,0,,"Detective Trap" is a bit weak, don't you think?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:27.19,0:20:29.24,Default,,0,0,0,,He is a detective,
Dialogue: 10,0:20:29.24,0:20:31.38,Default,,0,0,0,,but he tries to lead the criminals into traps, so—
Dialogue: 10,0:20:31.87,0:20:33.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe 'pseudo-detective'?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:33.92,0:20:35.97,Default,,0,0,0,,He feels kinda like a fake detective, so—
Dialogue: 10,0:20:38.09,0:20:40.01,Default,,0,0,0,,"Shady Detective Trap?"
Dialogue: 10,0:20:41.05,0:20:41.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:42.09,0:20:44.05,Default,,0,0,0,,It makes you wonder what kind of detective he is.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:44.05,0:20:45.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go with this.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:48.60,0:20:50.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Here you are.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:50.97,0:20:53.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Please take one.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:56.94,0:20:59.90,Default,,0,0,0,,It sure was a long wait.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:59.90,0:21:02.86,Default,,0,0,0,,But today you finally find \Nout the entries for the contest.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.90,0:21:02.86,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\an8\c&H8C8F86&\frz-18\fax0.1\blur1.003\fnHand Of Sean\fs42.117\pos(993.333,267.407)\fsp3.008}Entrants to the Golden Future Cup\N{\c&H555ADC&}Announced
Dialogue: 10,0:21:02.86,0:21:05.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Kinda gets you excited, huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:17.33,0:21:21.36,Default,,0,0,0,,If we don't get accepted into the contest,
Dialogue: 10,0:21:21.36,0:21:22.71,Default,,0,0,0,,serialization is out of the question.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:25.55,0:21:29.13,Default,,0,0,0,,And that goes for an anime too, of course.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:30.76,0:21:32.27,Default-Italic,,0,0,0,,And Azuki and my dreams.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:33.73,0:21:35.03,Default,,0,0,0,,It'll be fine.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:35.60,0:21:37.53,Default,,0,0,0,,It was really interesting.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:38.56,0:21:40.74,Default,,0,0,0,,The main character was really cool, too.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:42.40,0:21:44.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure it'll be fine.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:51.45,0:21:52.54,Default,,0,0,0,,It's Hattori.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:54.16,0:21:55.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi, this is Takagi.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:58.42,0:21:59.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:03.82,0:22:06.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Our entry into the contest is official!
Dialogue: 10,0:22:08.27,0:22:09.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright!
Dialogue: 10,0:22:09.51,0:22:12.93,Default,,0,0,0,,We did it! We did it! We did it!
Dialogue: 10,0:22:13.47,0:22:16.31,Default,,0,0,0,,This means our manga \Nwill be in the weekly Jack!
Dialogue: 10,0:22:16.31,0:22:18.26,Default,,0,0,0,,This is awesome!
Dialogue: 10,0:22:18.26,0:22:19.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so happy that I'm crying!
Dialogue: 10,0:22:19.90,0:22:21.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Congratulations!
Dialogue: 10,0:22:21.19,0:22:24.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll go buy some ingredients and make \Nsome curry for you guys to celebrate!
Dialogue: 10,0:22:24.94,0:22:25.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks, Miyoshi!
Dialogue: 10,0:22:25.86,0:22:26.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I love you!
Dialogue: 10,0:22:27.40,0:22:28.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Saiko, you—
Dialogue: 10,0:22:30.37,0:22:32.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Saiko, before that,
Dialogue: 10,0:22:32.83,0:22:34.45,Default,,0,0,0,,you've gotta message Miho.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:34.45,0:22:36.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, that's right.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:36.01,0:22:39.16,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong? You forget because \Nyou're cheating with Miyoshi?
Dialogue: 10,0:22:39.16,0:22:40.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't forget.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:40.29,0:22:41.33,Default,,0,0,0,,And I'm not cheating.
